  "texts": [
    "We evaluate pretrained models through in-context learning using the lm-evaluation-harness framework [11], reporting accuracy as the primary metric.",
    "The evaluation suite spans three task categories with 13 benchmarks: (1) General Knowledge-ARC [7], BoolQ [6],CommonsenseQA [26], MMLU [13], and SciQ [30]; (2) Reasoning-COPA [12], HellaSwag [31], PIQA [4], SIQA [23], and WinoGrande [22]; (3) Reading Comprehension-CoQA [21], LAMBADA [17], and OpenBookQA [16].",
    "Further evaluation details are provided in Appendix D.Baseline Datasets.",
    "We compare AICC against three strong baselines:1.",
    "TfCC: Applies Trafilatura extraction to the same CC snapshots with identical post-processing (Section 4.1)."
  ],
